        #_R_56758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: flex; }
        iframe { max-width: 100vw; }
      }</style></div></div></div><div class="mb-4 hidden pb-5 md:block"><div class="py-2 text-center text-xs uppercase">Advertisement</div><div class="flex w-full flex-nowrap justify-center"><div class="flex ad-container" id="_R_96758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_"><div class="hidden" id="_R_96758qoqk5elubsnqq5b_"></div><div class="flex size-full items-center justify-center text-center leading-3 bg-marshmallow dark:bg-ramones dark:text-grey-hair" style="height:250px;width:300px">Advertisement</div><style type="text/css">#_R_96758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: none; }
@media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
        #_R_96758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: flex; }
        iframe { max-width: 100vw; }
      }</style></div></div></div><p class="mb-4 text-lg md:leading-8 break-words">So, when the Wachowskis missed out on their man it wasn't an instant decision to then pursue Reeves. No, the role was turned down by <a href="https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/tagged/nicolas-cage" data-ylk="slk:Nicolas Cage;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" data-yga="{&quot;yLinkElement&quot;:&quot;context_link&quot;,&quot;yModuleName&quot;:&quot;content-canvas&quot;,&quot;yLinkText&quot;:&quot;Nicolas Cage&quot;}" class="link ">Nicolas Cage</a> too. His reasons were more logistical.</p><p class="mb-4 text-lg md:leading-8 break-words">“There was a couple of movies that I was offered, but I had good reasons so couldn't do it,” <a href="http://www.mtv.com/news/2429509/how-nicolas-cage-nearly-starred-in-the-matrix-and-lord-of-the-rings/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:Cage told MTV;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" data-yga="{&quot;yLinkElement&quot;:&quot;context_link&quot;,&quot;yModuleName&quot;:&quot;content-canvas&quot;,&quot;yLinkText&quot;:&quot;Cage told MTV&quot;}" class="link ">Cage told MTV</a>. “One was <em>The Matrix,</em> and <em>The Lord of the Rings. </em>Both are great movies, but they were shot in New Zealand for great quantities of time, I mean years. Well, Australia was<em> The Matrix. </em>But I had family obligations, so I'm glad I stayed and I had those experiences with my family,” he finished.</p><figure class="relative mb-4"><div class="relative"><img alt="US actor Nicolas Cage speaks during a press conference for his new movie &amp;quot;Jiu Jitsu&amp;quot; in the Cypriot capital Nicosia on June 29, 2019. - The movie is currently being filmed in Cyprus. (Photo by Iakovos Hatzistavrou / AFP)        (Photo credit should read IAKOVOS HATZISTAVROU/AFP/Getty Images)" loading="lazy" width="960" height="641" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-lg" style="color:transparent" src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/P5SJrW0EWYGhD53a7lvMxQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-images/2019-07/01335d10-a4b5-11e9-bbff-4093a44cfdb9"/><button aria-label="View larger image" class="group absolute bottom-0 size-full" data-ylk="elm:expand;itc:1;sec:image-lightbox;slk:lightbox-open;"><span class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 rounded-full bg-white p-3 opacity-100 shadow-elevation-3 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:block group-hover:opacity-100 md:p-[17px] lg:bottom-6 lg:right-6 lg:bg-white/90 lg:p-5 lg:opacity-0 lg:shadow-none"><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" aria-hidden="true" class="size-4 lg:size-6" width="22" height="22"><path d="M12.372.92c0-.506.41-.916.915-.916L21 0l-.004 7.712a.917.917 0 0 1-1.832 0V3.183l-6.827 6.828-1.349-1.348 6.828-6.828h-4.529a.915.915 0 0 1-.915-.915M1.835 17.816l6.828-6.828 1.349 1.349-6.829 6.827h4.529a.915.915 0 0 1 0 1.831L0 21l.004-7.713a.916.916 0 0 1 1.831 0z"></path></svg></span></button><dialog aria-label="Modal dialogue" aria-modal="true" class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 top-0 z-4 size-full max-h-none max-w-none bg-white hidden"></dialog></div><figcaption class="relative text-sm mt-1 pr-2.5"><div style="max-height:none;overflow:visible">It could've been Cage. (Photo by IAKOVOS HATZISTAVROU/AFP/Getty Images)</div></figcaption></figure><p class="mb-4 text-lg md:leading-8 break-words">It was at this point esteemed producer Lorenzo di Bonaventura, who was an exec at Warner Bros. at the time, admitted things were getting desperate. Which led them to consider changing the gender of Neo, as they offered the role to <a href="https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/tagged/sandra-bullock" data-ylk="slk:Sandra Bullock;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" data-yga="{&quot;yLinkElement&quot;:&quot;context_link&quot;,&quot;yModuleName&quot;:&quot;content-canvas&quot;,&quot;yLinkText&quot;:&quot;Sandra Bullock&quot;}" class="link ">Sandra Bullock</a>, the co-lead in the Reeves starring thriller<em> Speed.</em></p><p class="mb-4 text-lg md:leading-8 break-words">“We went to so many people I don't remember, we were getting desperate,” <a href="https://www.thewrap.com/the-matrix-filmmakers-wanted-sandra-bullock-as-neo-before-keanu-reeves-took-the-role/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:di Bonaventura told The Wrap;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" data-yga="{&quot;yLinkElement&quot;:&quot;context_link&quot;,&quot;yModuleName&quot;:&quot;content-canvas&quot;,&quot;yLinkText&quot;:&quot;di Bonaventura told The Wrap&quot;}" class="link ">di Bonaventura told The Wrap</a>. “We went to Sandy Bullock and said we'll change Neo to a girl. Joel Silver and I worked with her on<em> Demolition Man</em> and she continues to be a very good friend of mine. We sent her the script to see if she was interested in it and if she was we would try to make the change. It just wasn't something for her at the time, so it didn't go anywhere.”</p><div class="max-md:faux-bleed mb-4 bg-marshmallow pb-5 dark:bg-ramones md:invisible md:mb-0 md:h-0 md:overflow-hidden md:pb-0"><div class="py-2 text-center text-xs uppercase">Advertisement</div><div class="flex w-full flex-nowrap justify-center"><div class="flex ad-container" id="_R_59758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_"><div class="hidden" id="_R_59758qoqk5elubsnqq5b_"></div><div class="flex size-full items-center justify-center text-center leading-3 bg-marshmallow dark:bg-ramones dark:text-grey-hair" style="height:250px;width:300px">Advertisement</div><style type="text/css">#_R_59758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: none; }
@media screen and (max-width: 767.95px) {
        #_R_59758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: flex; }
        iframe { max-width: 100vw; }
      }</style></div></div></div><div class="mb-4 hidden pb-5 md:block"><div class="py-2 text-center text-xs uppercase">Advertisement</div><div class="flex w-full flex-nowrap justify-center"><div class="flex ad-container" id="_R_99758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_"><div class="hidden" id="_R_99758qoqk5elubsnqq5b_"></div><div class="flex size-full items-center justify-center text-center leading-3 bg-marshmallow dark:bg-ramones dark:text-grey-hair" style="height:250px;width:300px">Advertisement</div><style type="text/css">#_R_99758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: none; }
@media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
        #_R_99758qoqk5elubsnqq5bH1_ { display: flex; }
        iframe { max-width: 100vw; }
      }</style></div></div></div><p class="mb-4 text-lg md:leading-8 break-words">In this same interview, di Bonaventura admitted that there were other high-profile names he wanted to take on this seemingly unpopular role, but once again, they turned their nose up at the production.</p><iframe class="mb-4" height="auto" loading="lazy" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/D4eJx-0g3Do" style="aspect-ratio:1.78" title="youtube embed content" width="100%"></iframe><p class="mb-4 text-lg md:leading-8 break-words">“The first movie star who says is <a href="https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/tagged/brad-pitt" data-ylk="slk:Brad Pitt,;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" data-yga="{&quot;yLinkElement&quot;:&quot;context_link&quot;,&quot;yModuleName&quot;:&quot;content-canvas&quot;,&quot;yLinkText&quot;:&quot;Brad Pitt,&quot;}" class="link ">Brad Pitt,</a> he's doing <em>Seven Years in Tibet </em>and then he's coming out of it and he's way too exhausted to take this on, so he's gone,” he said.</p><div class="mb-4"><div class="mb-4" id="recirc-53a8586b-452f-3ec1-b454-abbe11255798"><div class="mb-3.5 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 22 22" aria-hidden="true" width="24" height="24"><path stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M12.24 3.84 16.35.72m-6.28 3.12L5.96.72"></path><path fill="#979EA8" stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M11.17 7.99a2.59 2.59 0 1 0 0-5.18 2.59 2.59 0 0 0 0 5.18"></path><path fill="#EAA300" stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M20.86 5.4H1.35a.35.35 0 0 0-.35.35v13.48c0 .193.157.35.35.35h19.51a.35.35 0 0 0 .35-.35V5.75a.35.35 0 0 0-.35-.35"></path><path fill="#979EA8" stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M3.07 19.58h16.08L18.81 21H3.42z"></path><path fill="#F7EFCD" stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M14.22 7.36H3.88c-.39 0-.73.27-.8.66-.55 2.96-.55 6 0 8.95.07.38.41.66.8.66h10.34c.39 0 .73-.27.8-.66.55-2.96.55-6 0-8.95a.815.815 0 0 0-.8-.66"></path><path fill="#00B8E9" stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M18.18 10.3a1.42 1.42 0 1 0 0-2.84 1.42 1.42 0 0 0 0 2.84m0 4.12a1.42 1.42 0 1 0 0-2.84 1.42 1.42 0 0 0 0 2.84"></path><path stroke="#0C0713" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.8" d="M16.75 16.13h2.85m-2.85 1.5h2.85"></path></svg><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-5">More in Entertainment</h2></div><div class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-rows-[auto_auto_1fr]"><div class="relative flex lg:flex-col lg:row-span-3"><div class="relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden mr-3 size-[110px] rounded-lg lg:h-[200px] lg:mb-3 lg:mr-0 lg:w-full"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="0" height="0" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="size-full object-cover" style="color:transparent" src="https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/RUSKO3DqOPM0yes_MT5w9Q--~B/Zmk9c3RyaW07aD00MDA7cT05NTt3PTYyNDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/evening_standard_239/497b8b1412b870e14142edebdda50840.cf.webp"/></div><div><h3 class="mb-1.5 text-[1.0625rem] font-semibold lg:text-xl lg:leading-[1.625rem]"><a data-ylk="ct:story;elm:hdln;g:d03849e1-dfd0-35a2-bcda-43f08cfdb36e;itc:0;sec:trending-story-center;ll3:target-deeplink;" href="https://uk.news.yahoo.com/reason-behind-naga-munchettys-sly-095322240.html" class="stretched-box line-clamp-3 text-primary">Revealed: Reason behind Naga Munchetty&#x27;s &#x27;sly digs&#x27; at Carol Kirkwood as star leaves BBC Breakfast</a></h3><div class="flex w-full flex-row items-center truncate"><div class="flex flex-row items-center"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mr-1.5 inline size-5 rounded-full" style="color:transparent" src="https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/AOQEA9bt.uBt3y27kGTHTg--~B