 one {{value} item} other {{value} items}}\",\"mail.SENDER\":\"From your inbox\",\"marchmadness.MENS_BRACKET\":\"Fill out men's bracket\",\"marchmadness.WOMENS_BRACKET\":\"Fill out women's bracket\",\"marchmadness.BEAT_THE_BUZZER\":\"Beat the Buzzer\",\"marchmadness.FILL_OUT_BRACKET\":\"Fill out a bracket and invite your crew to the mayhem.\",\"marchmadness.TURN_BRACKETS\":\"Turn your brackets into $50K\",\"marchmadness.ENTER_FOR_CHANCE\":\"Enter your bracket for a chance to win $25K in both tournaments.\",\"marchmadness.BRACKET_MAYHEM\":\"Bracket mayhem\",\"marchmadness.CREATE_A_BRACKET\":\"Fill out a bracket\",\"marchmadness.BRACKETS_OPEN_MARCH_15\":\"Brackets are now open\",\"marchmadness.SEE_DETAILS\":\"See details\",\"marchmadness.CHECK_YOUR_BRACKET\":\"Check your bracket\",\"marchmadness.CHECK_YOUR_BRACKETS_PLURAL\":\"Check your brackets\",\"marchmadness.YOU_HAVE_N_BRACKETS\":\"You have {count} brackets\",\"marchmadness.OPTION_STILL_OPEN\":\"{gender}'s brackets are still open for you to shoot your shot at $25K\",\"monetization.AD_PLACEHOLDER\":\"Advertisement\",\"movie_rankings.METHODOLOGY_TITLE\":\"Methodology\",\"movie_rankings.METHODOLOGY_FIRST_PARAGRAPH\":\"Our formula considers four factors to generate a rating for each movie. Here they are, ranked from most to least important:\",\"movie_rankings.AUDIENCE_SCORE_TITLE\":\"Audience score:\",\"movie_rankings.AUDIENCE_SCORE_DESCRIPTION\":\"Do viewers like the movie?\",\"movie_rankings.INTEREST_SCORE_TITLE\":\"Interest score:\",\"movie_rankings.INTEREST_SCORE_DESCRIPTION\":\"Are people reading about, searching for it or leaving reviews for it?\",\"movie_rankings.CAST_SCORE_TITLE\":\"Cast score:\",\"movie_rankings.CAST_SCORE_DESCRIPTION\":\"How notable or award-winning is the cast?\",\"movie_rankings.RECENCY_SCORE_TITLE\":\"Recency score:\",\"movie_rankings.RECENCY_SCORE_DESCRIPTION\":\"Did it come out recently?\",\"movie_rankings.METHODOLOGY_FINAL_PARAGRAPH_PART_1\":\"For these first three metrics, if a film is in the top 15% of our Top 100 list, we give it a special badge. We use data from Yahoo and reliable movie sources including\",\"movie_rankings.METHODOLOGY_FINAL_PARAGRAPH_PART_2\":\"to calculate our scores, and only include films that received a wide theatrical or streaming release in the US in 365. Learn more about what goes into each metric in the\",\"movie_rankings.METHODOLOGY_FINAL_LINK\":\"full methodology.\",\"movie_rankings.SUMMARY_TITLE\":\"About\",\"movie_rankings.SUMMARY_TEXT\":\"We find the top 100 movies of the past year by calculating a score for every release, based on audience ratings, the star power of the cast and how much interest the film is attracting on Yahoo News and on Yahoo Search, with a little extra credit for movies that came out more recently.\",\"movie_rankings.DIRECTOR_TITLE\":\"Director\",\"movie_rankings.CAST_TITLE\":\"Cast\",\"movie_rankings.RELEASED_TITLE\":\"Released\",\"movie_rankings.MAIN_TITLE\":\"Yahoo 100:\",\"movie_rankings.MAIN_TITLE_FINAL_WORD\":\"Top movies\",\"movie_rankings.SUBTITLE\":\"Find your next watch with our ranking of the hundred best recent films.\",\"movie_rankings.RANKINGS_TABLE_HEADING\":\"Latest rankings\",\"movie_rankings.RANKINGS_TABLE_SUBHEADING\":\"Updates daily (latest:\",\"movie_rankings.TRENDING_BADGE_HEADING\":\"Trending\",\"movie_rankings.TRENDING_BADGE_TOOLTIP\":\"Highly searched for and read about on Yahoo.\",\"movie_rankings.STARPOWER_BADGE_HEADING\":\"Buzzy cast\",\"movie_rankings.STARPOWER_BADGE_TOOLTIP\":\"High cast interest on Yahoo or Oscars recognition.\",\"movie_rankings.AUDIENCE_BADGE_HEADING\":\"Audience choice\",\"movie_rankings.AUDIENCE_BADGE_TOOLTIP\":\"Highly rated by viewers of the movie.\",\"movie_rankings.OSCAR_NOMINEE_BADGE_HEADING\":\"Academy Award nominee\",\"movie_rankings.OSCAR_NOMINEE_BADGE_TOOLTIP\":\"Nominated for {nominationCount} Academy Award{nominationCount, plural, one {} other {s}}.\",\"movie_rankings.OSCAR_WINNER_BADGE_HEADING\":\"Academy award winner\",\"movie_r